Version:
  20111107: Original version
  20111109: Fix bugs and redesign the gui
  20111111: Deprecate drawing png with cairo (without anti-alias)

Installation:
    0. Be sure have conky compiled with lua and luacairo
    1. Be sure have wget
    2. Extrac this.zip to $HOME directory
    3. Make a soft link $HOME/.conkyrc -> $HOME/.conky/conkyrc

